					<p>
						Cubana Lounge and ArtKids® Holland welcome you to our very first Cubana~Artkids® Talent showcase; happening on the 17th of Dec. 2022 @Cubana Lounge Owerri.
					</p>
				</article>
			</div>
			<hr />
			<!-- Footer -->
			<footer class="p-4 flex justify-start items-center space-x-4">
				<Avatar src="/images/red-black-purple-gold-with-sun.svg" />
				<div class="flex-auto flex justify-between items-center">
					<h6 class="font-bold">By LastMessengerS</h6>
					<small>On {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</small>
